<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to StreamAPI Newsletter - API Access Granted</title>
    <style>
        /* Email-specific styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #f8f9fa;
            background-color: #1a202c;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #2d3748;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .email-logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #10b981;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .email-body {
            background-color: #374151;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #10b981;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .social-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        hr {
            border: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: #4b5563;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .content-section {
            background-color: #2d3748;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .movie-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .movie-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .movie-item img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .movie-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }
        .api-access-box {
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #10b981;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .api-key-box {
            background: #2d3748;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        
        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .feature-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .feature-item i {
            color: #10b981;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <div class="email-logo">
                <span style="color: #10b981;">&#9658;</span> StreamAPI
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-body">
            <h1>Welcome to StreamAPI!</h1>
            
            <p>Hello there,</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for subscribing to the StreamAPI newsletter! You now have access to our comprehensive API endpoints and will receive the latest updates on movies, TV shows, and platform features.</p>
            
