            <div class="content-section">
                <h3><span style="color: #10b981;">&#9733;</span> What's Next?</h3>
                <ul style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>üìö Review our <a href="https://streamapi-m8o1-802nxfyk2-botcoder254s-projects.vercel.app/api" style="color: #10b981;">API documentation</a></li>
                    <li>üîß Test the endpoints using Postman or cURL</li>
                    <li>üíª Integrate the API into your application</li>
                    <li>üì± Try our responsive video player</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= siteUrl %>" class="button">Visit StreamAPI</a>
            </div>
            
            <hr>
            
            <p>We're excited to have you as part of our community!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The StreamAPI Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Github</a> &bull;
                <a href="#">Twitter</a> &bull;
                <a href="#">Discord</a> &bull;
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> StreamAPI. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Created by <a href="https://github.com/BotCoder254" style="color: #10b981;">@BotCoder254</a></p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 11px;">
                This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you didn't subscribe to our newsletter, you can safely ignore this email or <a href="<%= siteUrl %>/unsubscribe?email=<%= email %>" style="color: #10b981;">unsubscribe here</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 